sentence.text: Haplotype GAT for G protein-coupled glutamate receptor signaling pathway markers rs2067011-rs2645339-rs762724 showed significance (P=0.0239), but such association did not remain significant after multiple testing corrections.ConclusionsOur data suggested that genetic variants in GRM6 are associated with high myopia.
